title: 2025 ProBowl | Main Event & Fundraiser Results
body_text:
THANK YOU.
Our ECD community is unquestionably closer than it's ever been. The numbers don't lie, contributions are plentiful, and comradery is beyond measure.
This was a historic 3rd consecutive event player participation hit 40-plus .. .. that's never, ever happened! But when you have such strong family inclusion - the Browns, Adams, Winstons, Tronolones, Megills, Hassaans, Londonos, Spengemans - everyone is guaranteed a grand ol' time. Even Jodie Lee Taylor & Michael Butler returned!
Again, THANK YOU so very much. 🙂
